&lt;p&gt;In addition consider having modern, good quality LED lighting to prevent eyes from straining.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://spectrum.ge/images/1_nWk3XjlxSIVbrrNbJ4GZgw.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;510&quot; height=&quot;289&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Greenery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
