&lt;p&gt;Having the areas to take a break from the working environment is a good option, but also consider,  using open/outdoor spaces purposefully.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://spectrum.ge/images/be57d5e363dff8c1f3bad5f94abb1af5.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;526&quot; height=&quot;324&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Material Selection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
